To have these templates show up in XCode 3.x:

1. Open terminal and run:

mkdir -p ~/Library/Application\ Support/Developer/Shared/Xcode/File\ Templates/GGTemplates

2. Create a symbolic link from your new folder to this repository (or, just copy 'GGTemplates' into the 'File Templates' folder)

ln -s (path to root of repo)/GGTemplates ~/Library/Application\ Support/Developer/Shared/Xcode/File\ Templates/GGTemplates

3. Vua-la! It should no show up when you try to create a new file in XCode (under User Templates)